@startuml
title 文化导览模式时序图

actor "用户" as User
participant "前端" as Frontend
participant "后端" as Backend
participant "MySQL" as MySQL
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "高德地图API" as Amap
participant "DeepSeekAPI" as AI

== 场景1: 点击文化导览 ==
User -> Frontend: 点击文化导览
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: POST /api/get-user (导航参数)
activate Backend
Backend -> Amap: 请求逆地理编码
activate Amap
Amap --> Backend: 返回地理位置信息
deactivate Amap
Backend -> Amap: 请求天气信息
activate Amap
Amap --> Backend: 返回天气信息
deactivate Amap
Backend -> AI: 生成导览内容
activate AI
AI --> Backend: 返回导览文本
deactivate AI
Backend --> Frontend: 返回导览文本
deactivate Backend
Frontend -> Frontend: 播放导览语音
Frontend --> User: 展示导览内容
deactivate Frontend

== 场景2: 查询区域信息 ==
User -> Frontend: 查询区域信息
activate Frontend
Frontend -> Backend: GET /api/getArea (经纬度, 用户ID)
activate Backend
Backend -> Redis: 检查缓存
activate Redis
Redis --> Backend: 返回缓存结果
deactivate Redis
Backend -> Amap: 请求逆地理编码
activate Amap
Amap --> Backend: 返回区域信息
deactivate Amap
Backend -> AI: 生成区域导览内容
activate AI
AI --> Backend: 返回导览文本
deactivate AI
Backend -> Redis: 缓存导览摘要
activate Redis
Redis --> Backend: 确认缓存
deactivate Redis
Backend --> Frontend: 返回导览文本
deactivate Backend
Frontend -> Frontend: 播放导览语音
Frontend --> User: 展示区域导览
deactivate Frontend

@enduml
